name: Open Frame
tagline: Providing modern browser capabilies to Microsoft Intenet Explorer (IE 7.x and 8.x)
body:
# Open Frame
***
Open Frame is an open-source version of [Google Chrome Frame](http://www.google.com/chromeframe) plug-in that provides modern browser capabilities to Microsoft Internet Explorer (IE 7.x and 8.x) through an IE plug-in. This project is backed by [Workday](http://www.workday.com) and will be supported through August 2015.

![Open Frame](http://www.google.com/images/icons/illustrations/chrome_frame-430.png)
